Title: Random
Description: ["Official music video for Handsome Kenya's song ", Random, ' which was on his 1st full album titled "Amnesia" that was released March 5, 2014. A special extended version of the music video was created for the web release on Victor Entertainment\'s official YouTube channel. In it, Handsome Kenya falls asleep on a weekly manga magazine and dreams that he\'s stuck inside the volume as he runs between all the different series, art styles, and scenarios.', '\n', '\n']
